nts with normal liver function.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/12861/', '', 'Ticagrelor, Betrixaban, Apixaban, Cilostazol, Rivaroxaban, Clopidogrel, Iloprost, Lepirudin, Acenocoumarol, Urokinase, Cangrelor, More', 'Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, Nitrous acid, Dexrazoxane, Oxygen, Difelikefalin, Levoleucovorin, Arginine, Methionine, Deferiprone, More', 1767369485);
